title: 'Westworld' Season 4, Episode 8 Recap
description:
Joanna, David, and Danny break down the Season 4 finale of 'Westworld' by recapping the episode, asking 10 big questions about Season 4, pondering the likelihood of a fifth and final season, and more.

Hosts: Joanna Robinson, David Shoemaker, and Danny Heifetz
Producer: Kyle Crichton
